Package views.gui

Contains graphical user interface elements.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddResourceDialog
    AddResourceDialog is simple class for creating window which allows adding resource to given task.
    Calendar
    Calendar is responsible of creation of main window.
    DatePicker
    A simple window for choosing date.
    EventDetails
    A window containing event details.
    EventManager
    views.gui.EventManager is responsible for creating of window which manages given event.
    ExportManager
    Creates a window for export functionality.
    ImportManager
    Creates a window for import functionality.
    JDateFactory
    Factory for simple DD.MM.YY date picking component.
    LoginManager
    Creates a window for user management options.
    Settings
    Creates a settings window.
    TaskDetails
    TaskDetails creates window responsible for showing details of given task.
    TaskManager
    TaskManager is responsible for creating of window which manages given task.
